        <div style="margin-top: 50px;">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0;">Developer/Builder History </h3>
            <p>Rocky Ridge is a project for Qualico Communities, which is among the leading real estate agencies in Canada. Situated in Winnipeg, the company has been building homes and properties for more than 70 years. Established in 1951, the company has already created over 40 communities all over Calgary in areas like Ambleton and Vermilion Hill. </p>
